text: Samsul Huda Bachchu is a Jatiya Party (Ershad) politician and the former Member of Parliament of Narsingdi-1. ==Career== Bachchu fought in Bangladesh Liberation war. He was elected to parliament from Narsingdi-1 as a Jatiya Party candidate in 1986. He was the President of Narsingdi District unit of Jatiya Party. ==Death== Bachchu died on 10 February 2016 in Narsingdi town, Bangladesh. ==References== Category:Jatiya Party politicians Category:2016 deaths Category:3rd Jatiya Sangsad members
title: Samsul Huda Bachchu
